cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.FL

This paper deals with the expressiveness of communication primitives in various calculi, which falls under the category of formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL). It also discusses pattern-matching and intensionality, which are topics related to logic (cs.LO) and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also explores the use of different communication media, which is a topic in distributed computing (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE).
